Package: linux-headers-generic-lts-backport-maverick
Architecture: i386 amd64
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-generic
Description: Generic Linux kernel headers
 This package will always depend on the latest generic kernel headers
 available.

Package: linux-image-generic-lts-backport-maverick
Architecture: i386 amd64
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-generic, linux-firmware
Description: Generic Linux kernel image
 This package will always depend on the latest generic kernel image
 available.

Package: linux-generic-lts-backport-maverick
Architecture: i386 amd64
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-generic-lts-backport-maverick (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Complete Generic Linux kernel
 This package will always depend on the latest complete generic Linux kernel
 available.

